---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Vacuum Heat Treatment Furnace Parts And Components" description="You need reliable vacuum seals and heating elements that maintain integrity under extreme negative pressure. Our specialized components for vacuum heat treatment furnaces are designed to minimize leakage.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Vacuum Heat Treatment Furnace Parts And Components</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You need reliable vacuum seals and heating elements that maintain integrity under extreme negative pressure. Our specialized components for vacuum heat treatment furnaces are designed to minimize leakage and maximize thermal efficiency in your workshop. You can count on our high-grade materials to provide the durability needed for critical aerospace and automotive components processed in your sophisticated vacuum systems today.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Industrial furnaces often face carbon potential fluctuations and thermal instability which compromise part quality. You need components that mitigate these risks effectively.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our accessories provide precise liquid feeding and stable thermal measurement. You ensure repeatability and extend the operational life of your heat treatment equipment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Precision Drip Feeders</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Atmosphere Control Probes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Specialized Radiant Tubes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Custom Thermal Insulation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Vacuum Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
